#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:96
#: 722a4fbd23df4a3e9753a56aae4d7b57
msgid ""
"On a CUDA machine (a Linux box with an NVIDIA GPU and a CUDA-enabled PyTorch"
" build), you should see something close to:"
msgstr ""
"在一台 CUDA 机器上（一台带有 NVIDIA GPU 且 PyTorch 启用了 CUDA 的 Linux 机器），你应当看到与下面相近的输出："

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:120
#: c434b3adf7de43df9ecbf3c2063533b3
msgid ""
"On a CPU-only machine (e.g. a macOS / Linux laptop) the ``cuda`` line reads "
"``not available``, the ``[CUDA]`` solve is skipped, and the backend-table "
"header reads ``(CUDA: not available)`` with ``cupy`` / ``cudss`` listed as "
"optional extras to install."
msgstr ""
"在仅有 CPU 的机器上（例如 macOS / Linux 笔记本），\\ ``cuda`` 这一行会显示 ``not available``\\ "
"，\\ ``[CUDA]`` 求解会被跳过，后端表格的标题会显示 ``(CUDA: not available)``\\ ，并将 ``cupy`` / "
"``cudss`` 列为可供安装的可选 extras。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:125
#: 3fb44bcb3d6b4579832ff7e4b7396804
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The exact L2 error depends on the mesh, but should be on the order of "
":math:`10^{-2}` — anything more than a few percent indicates a numerical "
"problem."
msgstr "确切的 L2 误差取决于网格，但应当在 :math:`10^{-2}` 量级——若超过百分之几，则表明存在数值问题。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:131
#: 49d4423ab8d34dc9b91ab5acba39de96
msgid ""
"**Why is the GPU run sometimes *slower* than the CPU run?** The smoke-test "
"mesh is intentionally tiny (:math:`\\sim` 100 DOFs). At this scale, the CUDA"
" solve is dominated by one-time overheads — context creation, JIT kernel "
"compilation, host↔device transfers, and ``cuSPARSE``/``cuSOLVER`` workspace "
"allocation — rather than by actual floating-point work. The first GPU call "
"also pays for CUDA driver initialization. Run a real-sized problem "
"(:math:`\\geq 10^4`–:math:`10^5` DOFs) to see the GPU pull ahead; see "
":doc:`../performance/index` for benchmarks."
msgstr ""
"**为什么 GPU 运行有时反而比 CPU 运行 *\\ 更慢\\ *？** 冒烟测试的网格是有意设计得很小的（约 :math:`\\sim` 100 "
"个自由度）。在这种规模下，CUDA 求解的耗时主要由一次性开销主导——上下文创建、JIT 内核编译、主机↔设备数据传输，以及 "
"``cuSPARSE``/``cuSOLVER`` 工作空间分配——而非实际的浮点运算。首次 GPU 调用还要承担 CUDA "
"驱动初始化的开销。请运行一个真实规模的问题（\\ :math:`\\geq 10^4`–:math:`10^5` 个自由度）才能看到 GPU "
"反超；基准测试请参阅 :doc:`../performance/index`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:143
#: c0f337f58f834ae3b7749c81703e06ec
msgid ""
"**Which solver does ``A.solve(b)`` actually use by default?** "
"``SparseMatrix.solve`` is inherited from ``torch_sla.SparseTensor`` and "
"called with ``backend=\"auto\"``, ``method=\"auto\"``. torch-sla's auto-"
"selector then picks, based on device and problem size:"
msgstr ""
"**``A.solve(b)`` 默认实际使用的是哪个求解器？** ``SparseMatrix.solve`` 继承自 "
"``torch_sla.SparseTensor``\\ ，调用时使用 ``backend=\"auto\"``\\ 、\\ "
"``method=\"auto\"``\\ 。随后 torch-sla 的自动选择器会根据设备和问题规模进行选择："

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:148
#: 3252c3316d864dca98bf0d169b93e518
msgid ""
"**CPU** → SciPy / **SuperLU** (``backend=\"scipy\"``, ``method=\"lu\"``) — a"
" direct factorization, fast and machine-precision for the sizes reachable on"
" CPU."
msgstr ""
"**CPU** → SciPy / **SuperLU**\\ （\\ ``backend=\"scipy\"``\\ 、\\ "
"``method=\"lu\"``\\ ）——一种直接分解法，对于 CPU 所能处理的规模而言既快速又能达到机器精度。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:151
#: 5ccfccb7d21f4c0ca9a7beb849b93e6b
msgid ""
"**CUDA, DOF < 2M** → **cuDSS** if available (``method=\"cholesky\"`` when "
"SPD, else ``ldlt`` / ``lu``); falls back to CuPy, and finally to the "
"PyTorch-native iterative CG."
msgstr ""
"**CUDA，自由度 < 2M** → 若 cuDSS 可用则使用 **cuDSS**\\ （对称正定时用 "
"``method=\"cholesky\"``\\ ，否则用 ``ldlt`` / ``lu``\\ ）；否则回退到 CuPy，最终回退到 "
"PyTorch 原生的迭代式 CG。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:154
#: 44c14e6933514b3594f9e9596f384516
msgid ""
"**CUDA, DOF ≥ 2M** → PyTorch-native iterative solver "
"(``backend=\"pytorch\"``, ``method=\"cg\"`` for SPD or ``bicgstab`` "
"otherwise) with Jacobi preconditioning, to stay within GPU memory."
msgstr ""
"**CUDA，自由度 ≥ 2M** → 采用带 Jacobi 预处理的 PyTorch 原生迭代求解器（\\ "
"``backend=\"pytorch\"``\\ ，对称正定时用 ``method=\"cg\"``\\ ，否则用 ``bicgstab``\\ "
"），以控制在 GPU 显存范围之内。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:159
#: 70fb03297d9543788964d581bd7d1a47
msgid ""
"So the smoke test above runs **SuperLU on CPU** and **cuDSS Cholesky on "
"GPU** (Poisson is SPD), not an iterative solver. To pick a different solver "
"explicitly, pass ``backend=...`` / ``method=...`` to ``solve`` — see "
":doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers`."
msgstr ""
"因此上面的冒烟测试在 **CPU 上运行 SuperLU**\\ 、在 **GPU 上运行 cuDSS Cholesky**\\ "
"（泊松问题是对称正定的），而非迭代求解器。若要显式选择不同的求解器，请向 ``solve`` 传入 ``backend=...`` / "
"``method=...``——参见 :doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:164
#: 635d56b4db914d8e9352b3b2b0d5a98e
msgid ""
"Every sparse-solver backend is provided by ``torch-sla`` — TensorMesh adds "
"none of its own. Backends reported as ``not available`` are not a failure; "
"they are optional ``torch-sla`` extras you can install when you need them:"
msgstr ""
"每一个稀疏求解器后端都由 ``torch-sla`` 提供——TensorMesh 自身不添加任何后端。被报告为 ``not available`` "
"的后端并不代表出错；它们是可选的 ``torch-sla`` extras，你可以在需要时安装："

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:169
#: eabf7a0d946b4a8a93f5275a310f086e
msgid ""
"**scipy** ``[CPU]`` — SciPy / SuperLU direct and iterative solvers; the "
"default CPU path, always available."
msgstr "**scipy** ``[CPU]``——SciPy / SuperLU 的直接与迭代求解器；默认的 CPU 路径，始终可用。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:171
#: 1af25b97601b4adea4142bfdf6483e48
msgid ""
"**pytorch** ``[CPU/CUDA]`` — torch-native iterative solvers (CG / BiCGSTAB),"
" always available and fully autograd-friendly."
msgstr ""
"**pytorch** ``[CPU/CUDA]``——torch 原生的迭代求解器（CG / BiCGSTAB），始终可用且完全兼容 "
"autograd。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:173
#: 29572a26571c4d69ae9abc19eabb08fc
msgid ""
"**eigen** ``[CPU]`` — a JIT-compiled C++ direct solver; needs a C++ compiler"
" on the machine."
msgstr "**eigen** ``[CPU]``——一个 JIT 编译的 C++ 直接求解器；需要机器上安装有 C++ 编译器。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:175
#: 0002cfa671b644c9975a0ca42dfc96c1
msgid ""
"**cupy** ``[CUDA]`` / **cudss** ``[CUDA]`` — GPU sparse-direct solvers "
"(``pip install torch-sla[cupy]`` / ``pip install torch-sla[cudss]``)."
msgstr ""
"**cupy** ``[CUDA]`` / **cudss** ``[CUDA]``——GPU 稀疏直接求解器（\\ ``pip install "
"torch-sla[cupy]`` / ``pip install torch-sla[cudss]``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:178
#: f8cf9ab4087344ea9a799346a5ec7cf2
msgid ""
"Run ``torch_sla.show_backends()`` at any time to re-check status. See "
":doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers` for guidance on choosing among them."
msgstr ""
"随时可运行 ``torch_sla.show_backends()`` 重新检查状态。关于如何在它们之间进行选择，请参阅 "
":doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:183
#: f9cbfcb90f364d038cc85f8702bfe3c3
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "故障排查"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:185
#: e58a732cb16249c7972b9293aeef5dc3
msgid ""
"**``ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'tensormesh'``** — the package "
"isn't installed in the active Python environment. Re-check "
":doc:`installation`."
msgstr ""
"**``ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'tensormesh'``**——该包尚未安装在当前激活的 "
"Python 环境中。请重新检查 :doc:`installation`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:189
#: 755f1354bb5a4e1a8e92eec50fda14a1
msgid ""
"**``ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'torch_sla'``** — install it with "
"``pip install \"torch-sla>=0.2.1\"``. torch-sla is a hard, import-time "
"dependency: :mod:`tensormesh.sparse` refuses to import without it, and every"
" sparse-solver backend is provided through it."
msgstr ""
"**``ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'torch_sla'``**——请通过 ``pip install "
"\"torch-sla>=0.2.1\"`` 安装它。torch-sla 是一个硬性的、导入时即需满足的依赖：缺少它 "
":mod:`tensormesh.sparse` 将拒绝导入，并且每一个稀疏求解器后端都是通过它来提供的。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:194
#: d6bdd0c1f2ba4537b72a88ea4fd8c177
msgid ""
"**Stuck on ``[CPU ] Poisson 2D``** — your PyTorch build may be downloading "
"``gmsh`` cache files on first use; subsequent runs are instant."
msgstr ""
"**卡在 ``[CPU ] Poisson 2D``**——你的 PyTorch 版本可能正在首次使用时下载 ``gmsh`` "
"缓存文件；后续运行会瞬间完成。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/verify_install.rst:197
#: 5b1f2e8e3bcf4fc4918e36c922e9f058
msgid ""
"**``L2 error`` ≫ ``1e-2``** — likely an issue with the mesh or PyTorch "
"build. Open an issue at `github.com/camlab-ethz/TensorMesh/issues "
"<https://github.com/camlab-ethz/TensorMesh/issues>`_ with the full output of"
" this script."
msgstr ""
"**``L2 error`` ≫ ``1e-2``**——很可能是网格或 PyTorch 版本存在问题。请在 `github.com/camlab-"
"ethz/TensorMesh/issues <https://github.com/camlab-ethz/TensorMesh/issues>`_ "
"提交一个 issue，并附上本脚本的完整输出。"

